songs.title: Turn It Up, Turn Me On
songs.album: A Collection of Rare and Unreleased Recordings
songs.lyrics:
[Verse 1]
I'm gonna live it up
I'm gonna let go
I'm not perfect baby
But I'm afull close
I'm gonna stop time
I'm gonna keep them guessing
I'm here to party baby
I'm not here to listen

[Pre-Chorus]
I just walked inside
And I already caught you looking at me
Bragin's not my style but what the hell
I'm feeling good
So put the speakers on eleven
Shake my body left and right
I'm not looking for forever
I just wanna dance tonight

[Chorus]
Turn it up, turn it up
Turn me on, turn me on
Turn it up
And its on
Here it is, here it is
Here it comes, here it comes
Turn it up, turn it up
Turn me on, turn me on

[Verse 2]
I'm gunna dish it out
I'm gunna have some fun
I'm not crazy baby
Unless you want some
I'm gunna roam around
Till I find the one
Who likes to turn it up
Who likes to turn me on

[Pre-Chorus]

[Chorus]

[Outro]
I'm gone
